---
const BRAND = "백조마케팅";
const PHONE = "1811-6828";
---
<footer class="section footer" style="padding-top:40px; border-top:1px solid var(--border)">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid stack-md" style="row-gap:var(--space-4)">
      <div class="span-7">
        <strong>{BRAND}</strong>
        <p class="muted" style="margin-top:8px; font-size:var(--fz-14)">분양 광고에 관한 안내와 상담을 도와드립니다.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="span-5">
        <div><strong>문의</strong></div>
        <div>전화: <a href={"tel:"+PHONE}>{PHONE}</a></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-top:8px; font-size:var(--fz-14)">
      <a href="/privacy">개인정보처리방침</a>
      <span class="muted"> · </span>
      <a href="/terms">이용약관</a>
    </div>
    <p class="muted" style="margin-top:16px; font-size:12px">© {BRAND}. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</footer>
